S.FORM: Chucky Brown sraral hya'ga sisyuw na NBA, wal malaxmisuq qaniy la. kawas te 1968, byacing te 2 ru 29 ryax qu hintgan nya, kinhulan nya ga New York, hiya ga mnanak na ppzuy mari waya, ru squliq ka ppkal mari waya. 201 kunbun kinwagiq nya, 97 kunkin kin'suw nya, hiya ga qutux nqu spzyang blaq na ppzuy mari NBA. kawas 1989 mnwayaw ppzuy mari ga, mzyup squ te qutux lahuy ru te magal squliq, galun nqu Cleveland Cavaliers.
